{"tid":136193,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel 處理器大幅砍價應對 AMD Ryzen","createTime":"2017-02-27T01:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T12:34:17.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8f8ae1fd643273a32eb594053053db5c6b9c31","tid":136193,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T01:25:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">Intel 處理器大幅砍價應對 AMD Ryzen<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.coolaler.com/threads/intel-amd-ryzen.342796/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com%2Fthreads%2Fintel-amd-ryzen.342796%2F&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=0d364153\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.coolaler.com/threads/intel-amd-ryzen.342796/</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\nAMD Ryzen 再過幾天（3/2）就會正式上市，除了有不少玩家準備入手之外，面臨威脅的對手 Intel 似乎在價格上也蠢蠢欲降。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/17/02/intel_cpu_cp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F17%2F02%2Fintel_cpu_cp.jpg&h=d0a6899c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近有消息，國外購物網站已經開始在調整價格，這個調降是還蠻全面的，從入門的 Pentium G3258 到最頂級的 Core i7-6950X，調降價格在15~300美元不等，當然最高300美的就是原本要價1599美元的 6950X，而 Kaby Lake 高階 i7-7700K 則是80美元調降，前一代的 Skylake i7-6700K 甚至降了140美元。可以參考以下列表，前面已經是調整後的價格。<br />\n<br />\nIntel Core i7-6950X ($1599 US) &ndash; $300 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i7-6900K ($999 US) &ndash; $200 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i7-6850K ($549 US) &ndash; $150 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i7-6800K ($359 US) &ndash; $140 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i7-5820K ($319 US) &ndash; $100 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i7-7700K ($299 US) &ndash; $80 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i7-6700K ($259 US) &ndash; $140 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i7-4790K ($279 US) &ndash; $90 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i7-7700 ($289 US) &ndash; $50 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i7-6700 (259 US) &ndash; $90 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i5-7600K ($199 US) &ndash; $70 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i5-6600K ($179 US) &ndash; $$90 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i5-4690K ($189 US) &ndash; $70 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i5-7500 ($189 US) &ndash; $30 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i5-6500 ($179 US) &ndash; $50 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i5-4590 ($159 US) &ndash; $60 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i3-7350K ($159 US) &ndash; $20 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i3-7100 ($114 US) &ndash; $15 Price Cut<br />\nIntel Core i3-6100 ($109 US) &ndash; $20 Price Cut<br />\nIntel G4400 ($49.99 US) &ndash; $20 Price Cut<br />\nIntel G3258 ($49.99 US) &ndash; $27 Price Cut<br />\n<br />\n雖然 AMD Ryzen 處理器公開測試尚未解禁（3/2 22:00），但就目前所看來的效能與價格定位對於 Intel 是有相當程度的威脅，以往除了僅世代交替的微幅跌降之外，現在也知道要害怕了，不管是哪一家的支持者，這種結果都是樂見的。"},{"pid":"23856c0fcb92e2d89034f28ef15d641fe5dd95c9","tid":136193,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"香港代理睬你有尾"},{"pid":"28e495dadfadc4e042095032555de880fac63025","tid":136193,"uid":5151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港代理睬你有尾</blockquote><br />\n咁咪唔好係香港買囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac1894e2b953bbaede8fa8d797bd950a15f46ec","tid":136193,"uid":40828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T01:31:49.000Z","msg":"Microcenter正常價錢，冇減過"},{"pid":"b33d32ea57f01044ad579d71ac09ad70f0cb0980","tid":136193,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T01:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港代理睬你有尾</blockquote><br />\n+刀已經有價"},{"pid":"9657eea9885c897255bbc5d3eaab9c968affc320","tid":136193,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T02:55:07.000Z","msg":"粒ᴜ要千五蚊美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾咩用咖？"},{"pid":"1b69811a581d07d69f84ef2ac24d771aef768e33","tid":136193,"uid":36651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:05:09.000Z","msg"